  "abstract": "There is global consensus that current climate is\r\nchanging, mainly due to the anthropogenic emissions\r\nof green house gases (GHG) (IPCC 2007b).\r\nAlso, there is widespread concern over long-term\r\nclimate changes and changes in climate variability\r\nthrough occurrence of extreme weather events\r\nsuch as cyclones, floods, droughts, sea level rise,\r\netc. Agriculture is one sector of the economy that\r\nis exposed directly and considerably affected by\r\nclimate and its changes...........",
